{"tid":809902,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"（港產片）有冇人有睇《告別之前》？","createTime":"2018-09-07T14:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:53:36.000Z","uid":21772,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f010e34fbcf355229c0422166955b70d2bad9b4","tid":809902,"uid":21772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"性格樂天的昕翹 (李靖筠 飾) 是一位新入行的社工，專門負責癌症治療小組的個案跟進工作。 她獲分發了三宗跟進個案，分別是生於小康之家但不幸患上血癌的小女孩欣欣和她的父母 (張繼聰 及 衛詩雅 飾) ；新婚在即卻突然發現腦內長了腫瘤的嘉純 (談善言 飾)；還有年屆八十，只剩最多一年壽命的獨居老太太蘭姨 (羅蘭 飾)。三位病人面對疾病都抱著不同的心態，但同時有一個共通點&mdash;&mdash;與死亡越走越近，距離跟摯愛告別的時刻也越來越近&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入到去發現社工幾乎淨係跟蘭姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483e691db743377bceccc98dc7eb9c1c415d9e61","tid":809902,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"無乜人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80334a048cda103dae6bf3a232e604a65730153","tid":809902,"uid":115724,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"好眼淺 3條線都喊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a36ad779f5d7cca021e2956767e8aa83653022","tid":809902,"uid":174166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d531d2e021c2b2de82ae39b352ff7b220d557634","tid":809902,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"最尾睇到喊左<br />\n細路女果條線好感動"},{"pid":"c1b5bb0bf5b5f8b2f3e9d16c875bf985344c6e52","tid":809902,"uid":21772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2a36ad779f5d7cca021e2956767e8aa83653022","tid":809902,"uid":174166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018